{"tid":654692,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣嚮停車場兜圈","createTime":"2018-05-06T00:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T19:12:13.000Z","uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cddcd2fe2926398dfd38b713c9285ee475417c7e","tid":654692,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:07:55.000Z","msg":"嚮多層停車場<br />\n例如林士街<br />\n你入咗去基本上只可以每層兜一半咁一直轉上去搵位<br />\n佢道路設計係無預你兜哂全層先上上一層<br />\n因為你兜到另外嗰半邊就遇到不准進入牌上唔到上一層<br />\n你夾硬逆線先可以再上上一層<br />\n佢設計係只俾你兜半層就上上一層<br />\n另外嗰半邊係你落番來嗰時先好去架喎<br />\n你又無得嚮離場路線番轉頭上番去<br />\n譬如你6樓攞車走人<br />\n去到5樓諗諗下唔係都係要泊番架車上6樓再搞啲嘢<br />\n係唔得架<br />\n有啲場可以嚮最低層番轉頭上去<br />\n好多場焗你一定要走人架喇 (除非離開時搵到下層有位)<br />\n或者明知見牌都違規逆線或過雙白當自己剛入場咁樣<br />\n請問點解會咁架？我有無理解錯個啲停車場設計？"},{"pid":"58f356c955c875d9105a56bb78feddbaf6792e00","tid":654692,"uid":6018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"呢個場起碼5樓開始先叫做有d位"},{"pid":"272ab07462a789c82565eb92ead17bba6714edb7","tid":654692,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:27:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d655cc94093f6b3a44f3627489faadea3cce72f0","tid":654692,"uid":151728,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"272ab07462a789c82565eb92ead17bba6714edb7","tid":654692,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:27:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:28:04.000Z","msg":"你唔出聲係咪會死?"},{"pid":"bf99a9aa8214c4fbe557bbeff5f2010e884263d1","tid":654692,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58f356c955c875d9105a56bb78feddbaf6792e00","tid":654692,"uid":6018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"呢個場起碼5樓開始先叫做有d位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"我想問巴打係咪都發夢唔理逆線或不准進入標誌踩過去算數？<br />\n因為唔止喺呢個場<br />\n響其他場個設計都係咁<br />\n其實想知正常用法應該點搵位<br />\nP你有錯屌細力啲 pls<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b0c4e4823e194c24fb59e0eeb30bb9044e22b7","tid":654692,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T01:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個場起碼5樓開始先叫做有d位</blockquote>我想問巴打係咪都發夢唔理逆線或不准進入標誌踩過去算數？<br />\n因為唔止喺呢個場<br />\n響其他場個設計都係咁<br />\n其實想知正常用法應該點搵位<br />\nP<span style=\"color: red;\">仔</span>有錯屌細力啲 pls<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba163c7941f4b4d53b50848b9595c6b346325c2","tid":654692,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣禮頓中心<br />\n兜到老鍊咁高先有位，開頭見低層逆線有位但唔敢泊<br />\n出車又要兜番老鍊咁多層，個出口又多車，好耐先出到<br />\n不過應該同區最平+最易有泊車優惠"},{"pid":"83711764dcfe85a41e43d49d00d87908a99f1d1b","tid":654692,"uid":6018,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf99a9aa8214c4fbe557bbeff5f2010e884263d1","tid":654692,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58f356c955c875d9105a56bb78feddbaf6792e00","tid":654692,"uid":6018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"呢個場起碼5樓開始先叫做有d位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"我想問巴打係咪都發夢唔理逆線或不准進入標誌踩過去算數？<br />\n因為唔止喺呢個場<br />\n響其他場個設計都係咁<br />\n其實想知正常用法應該點搵位<br />\nP你有錯屌細力啲 pls<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"正常都會偷小小位既，當你4樓上一到5樓個層，如果選擇直行係不準進入，但如你見到個邊附近有位就直行囉<br />\n<br />\n當然你要睇下附近有冇車先行啦，如果撞左你奶野，你都知個場有幾多靚車，撞一撞都幾金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n始終P牌真係唔太建議咁做，出左事真係又加監又賠錢比人<br />\n<br />\n始終渣多半個圈唔會差太多時間，你諗後果啦，巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都知個場咁渣頭都暈，但6樓以上保證有位，同電梯行單雙數，要等電梯都唔會太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n渣多幾次去就熟嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa4ecf077a12d2534de5c4ff5fe522d419a7aa6","tid":654692,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83711764dcfe85a41e43d49d00d87908a99f1d1b","tid":654692,"uid":6018,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf99a9aa8214c4fbe557bbeff5f2010e884263d1","tid":654692,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58f356c955c875d9105a56bb78feddbaf6792e00","tid":654692,"uid":6018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T00:15:55.000Z","msg":"呢個場起碼5樓開始先叫做有d位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"我想問巴打係咪都發夢唔理逆線或不准進入標誌踩過去算數？<br />\n因為唔止喺呢個場<br />\n響其他場個設計都係咁<br />\n其實想知正常用法應該點搵位<br />\nP你有錯屌細力啲 pls<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"正常都會偷小小位既，當你4樓上一到5樓個層，如果選擇直行係不準進入，但如你見到個邊附近有位就直行囉<br />\n<br />\n當然你要睇下附近有冇車先行啦，如果撞左你奶野，你都知個場有幾多靚車，撞一撞都幾金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n始終P牌真係唔太建議咁做，出左事真係又加監又賠錢比人<br />\n<br />\n始終渣多半個圈唔會差太多時間，你諗後果啦，巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都知個場咁渣頭都暈，但6樓以上保證有位，同電梯行單雙數，要等電梯都唔會太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n渣多幾次去就熟嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"Thx 巴打認真答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我見呢個情況好似唔止林士街<br />\n其他領展即係前房署物業都係咁設計"},{"pid":"3cc990707ecd4a2d0899dc04717dfbd4515d25e8","tid":654692,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T19:12:13.000Z","msg":"大部分場如果單程上同落, 出閘前一定會有位比你上番去<br />\n就算係無回頭, 最多都係去到最低果部份好少路段先無得兜番上去, 仲會有牌寫住&quot;只往出口&quot;咁樣<br />\n唔會一向下兜就上唔番黎咁ON9"}]}